in my restaurant.

500
00:20:26,158 --> 00:20:27,825
That's what I've been
trying to tell you.

501
00:20:27,859 --> 00:20:29,827
It's not
your restaurant anymore.

502
00:20:29,861 --> 00:20:31,829
The deal your dad made

503
00:20:31,863 --> 00:20:34,599
