685
00:27:26,711 --> 00:27:27,811
Yeah.

686
00:27:27,846 --> 00:27:29,647
Wait a minute...

687
00:27:30,782 --> 00:27:32,716
Are you still upset
that I won that year?

688
00:27:32,751 --> 00:27:33,851
Don't be ridiculous.

