874
00:34:20,725 --> 00:34:23,660
I know, just...
So much to do.

875
00:34:24,662 --> 00:34:26,496
Lots to do, right...

876
00:34:26,531 --> 00:34:28,632
I understand.

877
00:34:28,666 --> 00:34:29,633
Take care.

878
00:34:29,667 --> 00:34:31,735
Take care, penny.

879
00:34:38,543 --> 00:34:39,042
