to be anyone's bff.

891
00:35:04,168 --> 00:35:07,938
The sooner I get
the restaurant on track,

892
00:35:07,972 --> 00:35:09,973
the sooner we can
return to our lives.

893
00:35:10,007 --> 00:35:13,610
I just need to
stay focused and be...

894
00:35:13,644 --> 00:35:16,546
The fixer.

895
00:35:16,581 --> 00:35:17,948
"The fixer?"

896
00:35:17,982 --> 00:35:19,916
Yeah, it's a...
It's a work thing.

897
00:35:19,951 --> 00:35:21,051
