to be good at this thing?

938
00:38:03,814 --> 00:38:05,448
Ugh, I need
to lie down.

939
00:38:05,483 --> 00:38:06,483
Okay, good luck.

940
00:38:09,553 --> 00:38:11,521
Just admit it.

941
00:38:11,555 --> 00:38:12,922
Nobody likes the food,

942
00:38:12,957 --> 00:38:15,859
